	<article class="post-631758 post type-post status-publish hentry category-financial-services category-legal tag-american-international-group-inc tag-boies-david tag-greenberg-maurice-r tag-paulson-henry-m-jr tag-starr-cos tag-subprime-mortgage-crisis tag-suits-and-litigation-civil tag-washington-dc per-boies-david per-greenberg-maurice-r per-paulson-henry-m-jr des-subprime-mortgage-crisis des-suits-and-litigation-civil org-american-international-group-inc org-starr-cos geo-washington-dc news_keywords-david-boies news_keywords-henry-m-paulson-jr-2 news_keywords-lawsuits news_keywords-maurice-r-greenberg-2 news_keywords-starr news_keywords-subprime-mortgage-crisis news_keywords-washington-dc-2" id="post-631758">
	<header class="postHeader">
